The paper deals with the automated measurement and analysis of vasculature in medical and pre-clinical images using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Convolutional Long Short-Term Memory units (ConvLSTM). This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the use of CNNs and ConvLSTM also suggests that the paper may belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), and Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
